metadata.name: Giving 6ack to the Industry By Alexander Harold
metadata.description:
An exclusive photo from the set of 6lack ft. J Cole's "Pretty Little Fears" Video Shoot. 
This is a 1 of 1 photo and is the same photo on the RIAA Certified Platinum Plaque (Over Million Copies Sold For This Song).
This photo was taken at the now closed "Fantasy Island" in Buffalo, NY. The music video has over 125 million views.

Part of the profit will go to supporting artists being consulted by Black Brooklyn, assisting with minting and gas fees!
